skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: the tech shuttle tracker
des: Provide real-time updates on where the MIT Tech Shuttle is. Supports only one request - where is the tech shuttle - which tells you the location of the shuttles (i.e. distance to their next stop) if actively available on NextBus at that time. This means it is subject to the same availability / accuracy constraints as mobi.mit.edu.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
